bug.short_desc: Comments section in /reviewlog is missing background color

assigned_to.name: Nobody; OK to take it and work on it

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 524249 screenshot
steps to reproduce: 1. Load https://addons.allizom.org/en-US/editors/reviewlog 2. Notice the log entry "Apr 6, 2011 1:21:33 PM Add-on has been deleted. minime" 3. Click on 'Show comments'
observed behavior: review comments are missing their background color. Check https://addons-next.allizom.org/en-US/editors/reviewlog for correct behavior.
This is probably a regression from Bug 646213
